title: Saajan
subTitle: Breaking conventional barriers, a poor, disabled orphan befriends the son of a wealthy businessman. However, their friendship is put to the test after both friends fall in love with the same woman.

title: Shriman Shrimati
subTitle: Appalled by the numerous problems faced by middle-class families, a wealthy couple decide to forsake their luxuries and live among the common people to make a difference in society.

title: The Legend of Bhagat Singh
subTitle: Born in British India, Bhagat Singh witnesses numerous atrocities during his childhood and grows up to become one of the most fearless freedom fighters in the country.

title: Hum Kisi Se Kum Nahin
subTitle: When Munna Bhai, a notorious gangster, meets Komal, he is immediately smitten. However, he must first confront her protective brother, Dr. Rastogi and her current boyfriend, Raja.

title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fianc√© plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.

title: Dulhan Hum Le Jayenge
subTitle: Sapna is raised by her three uncles, each one of them with a contrasting pursuit in life. She falls in love with Raja, who tries to impress each of her uncles in a different manner.

title: Deewana
subTitle: A newlywed Kajal gets widowed when her husband, Ravi, is killed by his enemies. She moves to another city and gets married to Raja, but her life takes a turn when Ravi returns from the dead.

title: Swarag Se Sunder
subTitle: Two brothers struggle to keep their family together as external forces like the younger brother's father-in-law try to break them apart.

title: Singham Returns
subTitle: Bajirao Singham, an honest police officer, encounters Babaji, a god-man with connections to high profile politicians, when he investigates the death of an officer from his team.

title: Singham Returns
subTitle: Bajirao Singham, an honest police officer, encounters Babaji, a god-man with connections to high profile politicians, when he investigates the death of an officer from his team.

title: Sauda
subTitle: Jyoti and Deepak fall in love and get married to each other. However, due to several misunderstandings and financial troubles, they get separated.

title: Hera Pheri
subTitle: Vijay and Ajay make a living by stealing money from people. Their friendship is affected when Vijay discovers that Ajay's father may have been his father's killer.

title: Thanedaar
subTitle: Orphaned and separated at a young age, two brothers grow up in opposing dimensions of society, only to cross paths years later as a policeman and a criminal.

title: Farz
subTitle: A veteran police officer becomes increasingly agitated when his partner is killed in the line of duty. To add to his woes, his daughter falls in love with his new daredevil partner.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Kachche Dhaage
subTitle: Stepbrothers Aftab and Jai, who loathe each other, must learn to put aside their differences and work together to prove their innocence in a terrorism case.

title: Welcome
subTitle: Two thugs meet Rajiv, who belongs to a respectable family, and want to fix their sister's wedding with him. However, when Rajiv's uncle refuses to the match, a series of hilarious situations occur.

title: Son of Sardaar
subTitle: Jaswinder returns to his hometown to sell a piece of land he owns and falls in love with a young woman only to find out later that her family wants him dead.

title: Son of Sardaar
subTitle: Jaswinder returns to his hometown to sell a piece of land he owns and falls in love with a young woman only to find out later that her family wants him dead.

title: Prahaar
subTitle: Major Pratap meets Peter during his training days in the Indian Army. However, when he is openly killed by thugs and no one seeks justice for him, Major Pratap takes matters into his own hands.

title: Auzaar
subTitle: Suraj, a police officer, is assigned to arrest his friend Yash, whose father runs an illegal business. He must now persuade his friend to make his father change his ways to avoid the consequences.

title: Deedar
subTitle: The marriage plans of Anand and Sapna are thwarted when it is revealed that Anand's business tycoon father had previously framed Sapna's father for a crime he did not commit.

title: Salaakhen
subTitle: An honest schoolteacher commits suicide due to the actions of the family of a man he testified against. In retaliation, his son takes the law into his own hands and seeks revenge.

title: Mard
subTitle: A police officer is punished for his honesty and transferred to an area controlled by a don. Challenging the gangster proves difficult for the cop due to the corruption of local law enforcement.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Movie
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Vardi
subTitle: Constable Bhagwan is killed by Lalchand, a gangster. Years later, Bhagwan's son Ajay, along with his father's close associate Inspector Verma, tries to capture Lalchand and bring him to justice.
